{"tid":2286524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"婚禮、本地遊續放寬 內地返港照免檢","createTime":"2020-11-15T05:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T05:23:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd0ed9a1c3ab5e16e606f55c5f487843bd5478b","tid":2286524,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201115/ETAD7AGPGVCWLPPU2CFRVF3SUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201115%2FETAD7AGPGVCWLPPU2CFRVF3SUI%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=4d27279b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201115%2FETAD7AGPGVCWLPPU2CFRVF3SUI%2F&h=c68b74b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201115/ETAD7AGPGVCWLPPU2CFRVF3SUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n婚禮、本地遊續放寬 內地返港照免檢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yLMhOHyD-NCr-HnLTM7MCKDW7k4=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5MAVZAHJWBD5FFSG4F4FZEHMTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyLMhOHyD-NCr-HnLTM7MCKDW7k4%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5MAVZAHJWBD5FFSG4F4FZEHMTU.jpg&h=ec6c26e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府早前放寬婚禮人數上限至50人，如今疫情有惡化趨勢卻未收緊相關限制。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府一方面收緊社交距離措施，一方面又維持婚禮人數上限50人及旅行團人數上限30人，而記協原定今日舉辦的遊行則被禁。陳肇始被記者提問是否出於政治考慮，她推說有關拒批記協遊行「政務司司長辦公室已經講咗啦」，又稱鑑於武漢肺炎疫情影響，以及香港疫情非常緊張，且疫情有惡化趨勢，為保障公眾健康，衞生署不建議舉辦任何涉及大型群眾聚集活動，但未有正面回應有關措施是否與防疫措施矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：特定群組強制檢測今實施  醫生可指示病人驗毒 違者或囚半年<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始在記會上表示，本港現時「外防輸入，內防擴散」的措施均全面收緊，因此屬緊張狀態，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始稱進入「緊張狀態」<br />\n<br />\n記者問她政府會否押後即將實施的新加坡「旅遊氣泡」，以及「回港易免檢疫計劃」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問、。。。。。。。。。"}]}